channel.title: A few models ive been working on lately
channel.description:
Ok here they are a few models ive been workiing on lately, tell me if u wnat me too release.
Twin hooks:
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/twinhooks.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/ChineseTwinHookSword.jpg[/img]
credits: 10% google for trace image, 90% me for tracing and putting together.
Dual weapon (dont ask someone on my server requaested):
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/Dualweapon.png[/img]
Credits: 100% jagex. all i did was delete some and stick the models together than a bit of recoulouring
Machine gun: (not done yet)
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/machinggunside.jpg[/img]
credits: 10% google for trace image, 90% me for tracing and addming together.
Flying dragon shield: (may have posted before)
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/DragonSheild.png[/img]
100% me. From scratch with primitives.
armadyl sword:
[IMG]http://i697.photobucket.com/albums/vv332/Buddy_budster/armav2.png[/img]
70% me for blade and colours, 30% jagex for armadyl hilt.
i am currently working on my second gun model: German luger.
so ill be posting that soon.
Thanks, Buddy
www.buddyscape.webs.com
